995: astro-ph/9910145) earlier study are\nrendered impaired as their objections were based on misconceptions regarding\nrelativistic distance definitions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2004 21:07:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Sep 2004 22:11:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-13"}
