ors that generalise the conformal Laplacians of\nGraham-Jenne-Mason-Sparling. As background to these issues, we give an explicit\nconstruction of the deformation complex in dimensions n>3, construct two\nrelated (detour) complexes, and establish essential properties of the operators\nin these.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2004 01:41:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Nov 2004 02:15:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 19 May 2005 21:59:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
